CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 21, 1959, pg. A1 reads: "Nursery Opening - With Housing Authority Administrator Alfred L. Tronzo and Mrs. Valerie Watts, president of the sponsoring club (top left photo, third and fourth from left), women of Bedford Dwellings, known as Club 1213, opened a day nursery Monday...happy youngsters and their mothers- Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of women and children, including several girls wearing braided hairstyles, gathered in nursery in Bedford Dwellings
